DiskInfo.mui/MUIA_DiskInfo_Initial

    NAME
    MUIA_DiskInfo_Initial -- [I..], STRPTR

    FUNCTION
    Provide at initialization time a path to the disk.

    EXAMPLE
    Wanderer Info passes a "Volume:Disk" string.
    (because of its icon oriented nature, given that a volume
    icon is located at volume root in "Disk.info").

